entry.title: Combined summary - confirm 1e595b258d48a8badd07523cbd8a8d74c150803c
entry.summary: The email sender has been notified that their membership in the Bitcoin-development mailing list has been disabled due to excessive bounces, with the last bounce being on June 21, 2015. They will not receive any more messages from this list until they re-enable their membership. There are three more reminders before their membership is deleted. To regain access, they can respond to the message or visit the confirmation page, and they can also change their delivery options on their membership page.It is unclear why the email with the sender's Gmail account caused bounces with this list. If there are any questions or problems, they can contact the list owner for assistance.
